                            <p>After my interviews, and synthesizing the information, I was able to really nail down the type of user I should have in mind while designing. I made a series of journey maps then looked at the different positions of social media and competitive platforms within the space. Finally, I was able to build a persona as a stand-in for my compiled information.</p>
